{"tid":1595094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"愛支保釣「英雄」陳毓祥身亡23周年","createTime":"2019-09-26T01:29:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T21:57:23.000Z","uid":192517,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"6351f1fdffad6ff34b840c6977f94906403eecd0","tid":1595094,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T01:29:34.000Z","msg":"又新一年，當然又黎回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mfc-mbbhf3k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fmfc-mbbhf3k&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRl3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=c0fb32fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mfc-mbbhf3k</a><br />\n<br />\n今年香港人或多或少都覺左醒<br />\n佢既後輩狗賊長今年喺日本坐緊<br />\n唔係話幾大影響，但對反送中示威的確少左一入阻力<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口號已經係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油</span></span><br />\n唔是中國人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢呢一生人做既野已經可以話係廢既，諗落都覺得好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc7023a0560ae041752f48228553100a762f405","tid":1595094,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5203ce3b8c8dcbbebfc37dee7a59e8b68a2b9240","tid":1595094,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T10:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744dba9b688535e69e51029931af1ffd7c18e98e","tid":1